overview: An electrifying portrait of a young artist determined to live life on his own terms. Born Rashard Bradshaw, Cakes Da Killa is a 22 year old hip hop artist. As an openly gay man he is not your run of the mill rapper, but he just might be your new favorite.
tagline: Not your run of the mill rapper, but he just might be your new favorite
title: Cakes Da Killa: No Homo
